    <item>
      <title>德国经济停滞不前，年底才恢复增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/german-economy-only-expected-to-resume-growth-at-end-of-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[分析人士表示，德国将勉强躲过经济衰退，但要到年底才能恢复增长——这种萎靡不振的状况将持续下去，引发人们对这个欧洲最大经济体未来的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/german-economy-only-expected-to-resume-growth-at-end-of-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元走弱，因上田表示日本央行不急于加息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/yen-fluctuates-after-boj-stands-pat-says-it-s-watching-fx</link>
      <description><![CDATA[此前日本央行行长上田和夫表示，继 3 月和 7 月加息之后，日本央行并不急于再次加息，日元因此跌至当日最低点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/yen-fluctuates-after-boj-stands-pat-says-it-s-watching-fx</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 03:02:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
